
10 GOSUB 1000 : REM INITIALIZE
20 HOME       : REM CLEAR SCREEN
30 GOSUB 2000 : REM DISPLAY AND MOVE
40 GOSUB 3000 : REM PAUSE
50 GOTO 20    : REM START OVER

1000 REM INITIALIZE STARS
1010 DIM X(4) : DIM Y(4) 
1020 FOR I = 0 TO 4
1030 X(I) = 5 + 5 * I
1040 Y(I) = RND(1) * 24
1050 NEXT I
1060 RETURN

2000 REM DISPLAY AND MOVE STARS
2010 FOR I = 0 TO 4
2020 HTAB X(I) : VTAB Y(I)
2030 PRINT "*"
2040 Y(I) = Y(I) + 1
2050 IF Y(I) > 24 THEN Y(I) = 1
2060 NEXT I
2070 RETURN

3000 REM PAUSE
3010 FOR PAUSE = 1 TO 200
3020 NEXT PAUSE
3030 RETURN